---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../consts';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description={`Privacy policy for ${SITE.name}.`}
>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="dek">Last updated: May 4, 2026</p>

  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    {SITE.name} is a Japanese history publication. This site is designed to
    collect as little personal information as possible.
  </p>

  <h2>Information We May Receive</h2>
  <p>
    If you contact us, subscribe through Substack, or follow links to third-party
    services, those services may process information according to their own
    privacy policies. We do not sell personal information.
  </p>

  <h2>Analytics</h2>
  <p>
    We may use privacy-conscious analytics or Google Analytics to understand
    which pages are read and how the site performs. Analytics is used to improve
    the publication, not to identify individual readers.
  </p>

  <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
  <p>
    Some pages may include affiliate links to travel, lodging, tours, or books.
    If you click those links, the third-party provider may receive information
    about your visit.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    For privacy questions, contact us through
    <a href={SITE.substackUrl}>Substack</a>.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
